column5: anyone catch the show? I found it very entertaining, some real nice fish too!
I am watching it right now. Rerun i think.

yes i did see the show as well,and theywere hitting a few good size muskies on the lower ottawa river..  .did you see how fast they were trolling...and they only had 20ft of line out they were trolling right in the prop wash....cool
John is a good dude. Anything he does is worth watching.
Don't know John, but heard the opening tune playing on the tube so went over to the TV and changed the channel to something better.  Maybe Dimestore..?
dimestore! ha! are those guys still around?  John is a very knowledgeable fisherman, I really enjoyed the show
Good show and Moose the FNC guys have really improved the show and format this year. Been a great season so far, they are back to the good stuff.
